title: Foutouri (department)
text:
Foutouri is a department or commune of Komondjari Province in Burkina Faso.


== Cities ==
The department consists of a chief town :

Foutouriand 11 villages:

Bartiébougou-Fulani
Bontégou
Bossongri
Gourel-CowpeaHaaba
Kienkièga
Paagou
Paagou-FulaniPenkatougou
Tambiga
Tambissonguima.
